  /Shift+Option+Zoom+Increase+JogWheel            Reaper _WOL_SETSELENVHMAX                                                        // SWS/wol: Set selected envelope height to maximum
  Shift+Option+Zoom+Increase+JogWheel            Reaper  42381                                                                    // Envelopes: Move selected points up   0.2DB
                                
